snippet.title: mets2128
snippet.description: This is the channel where I throw down my 2 cents on NFL Football matchups, Wrestling ppv predictions, rant on manga, do a little cosplay convention blogging, trying some of the weirdest fast food items and snacks that I can find out there, and post playlists of my choice check it out and hear the word on the street from me
